colortag Plugin for DokuWiki

adds <colortag> syntax

The syntax is:

COLORTAG ::= '<colortag>' TAGS '</colortag>'
TAGS ::= TAG | TAG ',' TAGS
TAG ::= COLOR | COLOR ':' CHAR | COLOR ':' CHAR ':' COLOR
CHAR ::= <good char to display in the cell. for instance, '&bull;'>
COLOR ::= <color name or '#'-prefixed hex color code>

If there are two COLORs then the last one is foreground color.

All documentation for this plugin can be found at
https://jno.undo.it/colortag.zip

If you install this plugin manually, make sure it is installed in
lib/plugins/colortag/ - if the folder is called different it
will not work!

Please refer to http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugins for additional info
on how to install plugins in DokuWiki.
